<Document>
  <name>五台山 3 天古建深度(佛光寺+南禅寺朝圣)</name>
  <description></description>
  <Folder>
    <name>D1 北京 → 五台山(台怀镇)</name>
    <description>约 360km · 5h · 五爷庙+显通寺+塔院寺</description>
    <Placemark>
      <name>D1 行程连线</name>
      <Style><LineStyle><color>ff3539E5</color><width>3</width></LineStyle></Style>
      <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>116.659905,40.129109,0 115.506183,38.850787,0 113.600138,39.083099,0 113.600737,39.081498,0 113.601137,39.082598,0 113.600538,39.082699,0 113.601237,39.082398,0</coordinates></LineString>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>1. 顺义枫泉花园</name>
      <description><![CDATA[北京顺义出发 · 7:00 走京昆高速 G5<br/><br/>标签: start<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 116.659905, 40.129109<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=116.659905,40.129109,%E9%A1%BA%E4%B9%89%E6%9E%AB%E6%B3%89%E8%8A%B1%E5%9B%AD&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
