      <Point><coordinates>116.659905,40.129109,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>2. 保定服务区</name>
      <description><![CDATA[京昆高速中段休整 · 9:30 · 约 130km<br/><br/>标签: service<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 115.506183, 38.850787<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=115.506183,38.850787,%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8C%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
