      <Point><coordinates>113.600138,39.083099,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>4. 显通寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五大禅处之首 · 青铜殿 + 铜塔 + 无量殿(国内唯一青铜建筑群) · 必去 0.7<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600737, 39.081498<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600737,39.081498,%E6%98%BE%E9%80%9A%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
