    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 塔院寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五台山标志性大白塔(高 56.4m) · 转塔祈福 · 必去 0.6<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.601137, 39.082598<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.601137,39.082598,%E5%A1%94%E9%99%A2%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
