    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>6. 寿宁寺素斋</name>
      <description><![CDATA[台怀镇寿宁寺素斋 · 17:30 时段 · 11:30 也开 · 错过吃不上<br/><br/>标签: food<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600538, 39.082699<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600538,39.082699,%E5%AF%BF%E5%AE%81%E5%AF%BA%E7%B4%A0%E6%96%8B&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
