      <Point><coordinates>113.276327,39.022646,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>3. 龙泉寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[汉白玉石雕牌坊(山西第一) · 距佛光寺/南禅寺 25km · 加分项 0.3<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.578763, 39.060999<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.578763,39.060999,%E9%BE%99%E6%B3%89%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
