      <Point><coordinates>113.601737,39.083699,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 殊像寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[文殊菩萨最大铜像(5 层楼高 · 9.87m) · 加分 0.4<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.59734, 39.079597<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.59734,39.079597,%E6%AE%8A%E5%83%8F%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
