    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>6. 菩萨顶</name>
      <description><![CDATA[康熙乾隆行宫 · 108 级台阶 · 红墙黄瓦 · 加分 0.3<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.606035, 39.087902<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.606035,39.087902,%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%A1%B6&mode=car&src=wutaishan-trial">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
